Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 已经这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点挫折要顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为了恢复精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地享受一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋 为什么不用羽衣隐身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 A8-52
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,52 52…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那个位置是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这个位置哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂 桂木君！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 同一张票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好的位置 竟然出现重复票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站着搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木君 你坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找空位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有空位置的 拼座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 学生和老师这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人看到就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业摔跤·诺那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAG CANYON TOURNAMENT FAINAL即将开赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽 虽然这是好位置 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选手 入场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝方 秋川淳 见泽光针
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红方 石角 株木开藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋川可是这个级别中年轻的王牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的三泽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 用的是跟鹤马同样的招数哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完后也会说「哦~」呢 好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那杯才是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样 上啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置好 感到的魄力就是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的位置根本没法有这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴得这么紧 果然还是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师和学生靠得这么近…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤 很燃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤选手们 倾尽自己全力对战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的举手投足都能引发观众欢呼雀跃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并为之震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤这么燃 是因为大家的感情碰撞到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤不仅仅在于摔跤台上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁决比赛的裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持选手的工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有观众 都合在一起才是比赛的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家成为一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么你就是不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么认真地为你着想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特地为了你去买游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大家一起努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 篮球社被废社了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到废社 篮球社的队长一直是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你这届被废社了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你毁了篮球社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在 我感到会重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还有人 会被你的理想所毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯 你做过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都说想变强的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了篮球社 为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拚命地付出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真觉得是为了大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你…知道什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能看到结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.96,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑的烦恼倾诉室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这个级别很便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说昨天接到长濑老师的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你也有接到？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 明明就很希望她打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太啰嗦了点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可能很微妙 长濑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有前段时间那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早~上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开班会前 我有个提案给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.66,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞岛 马拉松大会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的舞岛马拉松 大家一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经帮大家申请参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啰 哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 大家凝聚到一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通点吧 普通点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么还找我谈心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还一脸开心的样子和我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要被说成坏人似的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好自私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自私了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮危险的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正式成为教师前能认清现实还是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 长濑老干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这帮浑身BUG的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明做什么都无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么了 四眼宅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臭屁个什么劲啊 游戏疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 宅四眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿都行吧 谁管那种家伙
