Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们错了 我们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 桂木君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下了通往结局的步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须按照我所写的行动 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好自私
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自私了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 长濑老干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这帮浑身BUG的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明做什么都无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑离开后
